Harel Recanati Investment House Ltd.






Co-Chief Executive Officer

                                    2007 - Prior                


Harel Insurance Investments & Financial Services Ltd.


                  Harel Insurance Investments & Financial Services Ltd. engages in insurance and financial solutions. It operates through the following segments: Life Assurance and Long-Term Savings, Health Insurance, Non-Life Insurance, Insurance Companies Overseas, and Capital Market and Financial Services. The Life Assurance and Long-Term Savings segment engages in the life assurance branches, as well as its activity in the management of pension and provident funds. The Health Insurance segment provides illness and hospitalization insurance, including personal accidents, dental, and nursing. The Non-Life Insurance segment is the sales of insurance policies in the motor vehicle which covers damages caused, including motor property, compulsory motor insurance, property and other branches and credit insurance for mortgages. The Insurance Companies Overseas segment offers company insurances in the health and non-life insurance sectors. The Capital Market and Financial Services segment refers to mutual funds management as well as securities management among private individuals, corporations, and institutional customers. The company was founded on April 20, 1982 and is headquartered in Ramat Gan, Israel.                




Senior Manager

                                    Prior                


Union Bancaire Privée


                  UBP is an active, fundamental research-based manager which employs risk management as an integrated and continuous process aiming to: preserve the firm’s capital base and viability; balance capital-preservation and capital-optimization; maximize client and shareholder assets; blend a risk-awareness culture into the corporate culture and meet regulatory and supervisory requirements at all times.The firm constructs absolute-return portfolios and manages mutual funds, funds of funds and hedge funds. They invest in North American, European and emerging markets equities, bonds and the money market.UBP's funds of funds provide strategies covering most investment styles, aiming to deliver above average risk-adjusted returns over the long-term.  Their structured products aim for absolute or relative returns while aligning risk management with client needs. Multi-management funds selection is driven by both qualitative and quantitative analysis.  The qualitative process is based on primary research. The quantitative analysis consists of segmenting performance profiles in different market phases, analyzing each fund using a proprietary tool and applying a weighting model to ensure diversification and to balance the final portfolio.                




Senior Manager

                                    Prior                


Discount Bank & Trust Co.


                  Discount Bank & Trust Co., a subsidiary of Union Bancaire Privée, UBP SA, is a company headquartered in Geneva, Switzerland, that provides banking services. On 10 Jul 02 Union Bancaire Privée, UBP SA acquired Discount Bank & Trust Co.                





