Ezer Mortgage Insurance Co. Ltd.

                    Ezer Mortgage Insurance Co. Ltd., part of Harel Insurance Investments & Financial Services Ltd., is an Israeli company located in Jerusalem that offers mortgage insurance. It was acquired by Harel Insurance Investments & Financial Services Ltd. from American International Group, Inc. on 23 Dec 09 for $35.50 million.                  




