Harel Finance Trade & Securities Ltd.

                    Harel Finance Trade & Securities Ltd., part of Harel Insurance Investments & Financial Services Ltd., is an Israeli company located in Ramat-Gan that provides Brokerage Services.                  




Director

                    Current                  


Harel Insurance Finance & Issues Ltd.

                    Harel Insurance Finance & Issues Ltd. is an Israeli private company. The firm provides life insurance services. Ronen Agassi has been the CEO since 2011.                  




Chairman

                    Prior                  


Harel-Pia Mutual Funds Ltd.

                    Harel-PIA is an active, research-oriented manager which performs continuous research on the macro and micro economic developments and trends in global capital markets.  The economists and analysts in the research department examine market data and provide fund managers with forecasts and surveys for various investment periods.The firm offers an extensive range of mutual funds including Shekel funds that principally invest in short-term shekel instruments, funds that principally invest in inflation linked or non-linked shekel securities including government and corporate bonds, funds that invest principally in overseas securities and foreign currencies and funds that invest principally in shares traded on the Tel Aviv Stock Exchange and world stock markets.Some of Harel-PIA's funds focus their investments in specific sectors such as hi-tech and real estate.                  




Non-Profit Boards ▾




Member, International Committee

