© BDICode - Harel Finance Holdings Ltd.     The page is loading, please wait....   BdiCode CofaceBdiCofaceAdvertising OptionsGalleriesContact Usעברית   aaaBdiCoface- ABOUT USManagement CofaceBdiBDICode 2015 Digital Edition Companies     Managers          IndexCome Lead with usRankings TablesArticles & Surveys indexCompanies RankingsLeading Managers   Harel Finance Holdings Ltd.    Shimon ElkabetzChairman of the BoardTal KedemCEO    For PDF profile press hereHarel Finance Holdings Ltd. ("Harel Finance") is the financial arm of Harel Insurance Investments and Financial Services Ltd. ("Harel Investments"). Harel Finance is actively involved in mutual fund, investment portfolio, and financial products management and focuses on offering solutions for all financial needs through a wide range of financial products and services to private, corporate, and institutional clients (long-term savings plans are offered by Harel Insurance). Harel Finance manages some NIS 39.4 billion* through its subsidiaries - Harel-PIA Mutual Funds Ltd., (100%), Harel Sal Ltd., (100%), Harel Sal Matbei'ot (100%), and Harel Finance Investment Portfolio Management Ltd., (100%). Harel Finance is owned by Harel Investments, which is a public company and one of Israel's largest insurance and finance groups. Harel Investments offers comprehensive insurance and financial solutions, including health insurance, non-life insurance, vehicle insurance, home insurance, liability insurance, mortgage insurance, credit insurance, life insurance, pension funds, provident funds, advanced study funds, mutual funds, investment portfolio management, ETN's as well as other financial services. Total assets under management of the Harel Group in insurance, pension funds, provident funds, mutual funds, ETN's, deposits, investment portfolios (net), and financial services totaled some NIS 185.1 billion (as of December 31, 2016), while Group shareholders' equity totaled some NIS 5.17 billion. Line of Business
Investment House – mutual funds, investment portfolio management, financial products, and ETN's
Established in 1977Harel PIA – Mutual Funds
Harel Mutual Fund Management is one of Israel's leading and most prominent mutual fund management companies. Harel PIA manages some 150 mutual funds, with assets under management of some NIS 17.8 billion (as of December 31, 2016), which are available in many investment mediums, thus offering the investing public a wide range of investment possibilities, both in the Israeli and foreign capital markets. 
Its reputation of many years, which is based on professionalism, innovation, dynamism, and excellence, allows the investor to benefit from a wide range of investment possibilities. Harel PIA is backed by an extensive research department, which regularly monitors macro-economic developments and trends in the Israeli and foreign capital markets. Harel's mutual funds consistently receive top-performance ratings, led by the advice programs of the various banks.Harel Finance – Investment Management
Harel manages investment portfolios for private clients, corporations, and institutions. Harel has been active in the capital markets for more than 40 years – a fact that endows it with rich experience and market leadership. Investing with Harel's investment managers allows the investor to benefit from the strength of the Harel Group, and the support and financial stability of one of Israel's largest companies. Harel has a long tradition of reliability, excellence, creativity and outstanding client support. Harel manages investments for more than 6,600 clients with a volume of assets under management (including interested parties and internal products) of some NIS 12.5 billion (as of December 31, 2016).Harel Sal and Financial Products
Harel Financial Products is involved in the management of ETN's. Through Harel Sal and Harel Sal Matbei'ot, the company manages some 100 ETN's and deposits totaling some NIS 13.2 billion (as of December 31, 2016) and allows the investor to link to key stock market indices in the Israeli and foreign markets.
Harel is also involved in structuring complex products. These products are offered to investors through non-traded OTC transactions based on client demand, as well through publicly traded issues. The Firm has the unique mathematical strength to offer and price complex financial products.
Harel Finance – "For Your Profit and Peace of Mind."
Harel Finance – "To Profit from Professional Service" – Harel Finance believes in professional service, and offers solutions expressly tailored to the personal needs of each client while considering their investment goals, investment horizon, risk appetite, liquidity needs, and tax considerations. 
Harel Finance – "To Profit from Expertise" – Harel Finance specializes in investment management. Its investment managers have solid experience in the capital markets and strive to maximize client returns, subject to relevant risk appetites. Investment decisions are made by Harel Finance's investment forums (including a special forum for foreign investments). Decisions of the forum are based on the various research departments, which prepare macroeconomic, microeconomic, sector and public issue analytical reports. 
Harel Finance – "To Profit from Flexibility and Quick Responses" – Harel Finance is constantly working to adjust its products and services to market developments. Harel's trade departments, analytical departments, investment, and marketing managers offer the client base quality, professional, dependable and quick service. At Harel Finance, client money is professionally managed, without compromise.* Net after offsets of mutual holdings and related parties.
